    "In addition, conventional FF often rely on predefined functional forms and parameters, which limits their accuracy in capturing diverse and dynamic molecular behaviors (Zhang et al. 2023).",
    "Efforts have already been made to implement AI in MD calculations and in MD trajectory analysis (Noé et al. 2020; Mouvet et al. 2022; Mudedla et al. 2022; Behler and Parrinello 2007).",
